1
00:00:07,705 --> 00:00:09,025
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:37,945 --> 00:01:43,065
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,985 --> 00:01:47,705
‎XIE RESIDENCE

4
00:01:47,785 --> 00:01:49,505
Xie Yanlai needs someone to wait on.

5
00:01:50,425 --> 00:01:52,145
Does it really need
so many of us waiting here?

6
00:01:52,225 --> 00:01:54,185
Yeah. Who does he think he is?

7
00:01:54,265 --> 00:01:55,105
Alright, alright.

8
00:01:55,785 --> 00:01:56,625
It's the head's order.

9
00:02:04,825 --> 00:02:06,065
What's going on?

10
00:02:06,145 --> 00:02:07,385
What are they doing?

11
00:02:14,625 --> 00:02:17,105
Xie Yanlai, what do you think
you're doing?

12
00:02:17,185 --> 00:02:19,025
Yeah. What's your problem?

13
00:02:21,185 --> 00:02:23,185
Who gave you the nerve
to talk to me like that?

14
00:02:34,865 --> 00:02:35,905
Say it again.

15
00:02:36,585 --> 00:02:39,145
Don't think you can bully me
because you're in power.

16
00:02:39,225 --> 00:02:40,665
Yeah.

17
00:02:40,745 --> 00:02:41,665
That's right.

18
00:02:41,745 --> 00:02:42,985
But bullying the weak

19
00:02:44,145 --> 00:02:45,545
is what you do best.

20
00:02:45,625 --> 00:02:48,785
Our clan doesn't accept
a worthless lad like you.

21
00:02:48,865 --> 00:02:50,545
Since you're the son of a courtesan,

22
00:02:50,625 --> 00:02:52,425
then smile like her. Smile!

23
00:03:00,505 --> 00:03:03,985
He's said to be more powerful
even than Young Master Yanfang.

24
00:03:04,065 --> 00:03:05,865
Now, he's the Imperial Guard Commander.

25
00:03:05,945 --> 00:03:07,705
The Grand Princess appointed him.

26
00:03:07,785 --> 00:03:08,665
With power,

27
00:03:08,745 --> 00:03:11,025
he may revenge
for his childhood grievances.

28
00:03:11,545 --> 00:03:14,265
Young Master,
by Young Master Yanfang's orders,

29
00:03:14,785 --> 00:03:16,505
your house has been made ready.

30
00:03:16,585 --> 00:03:17,545
I'll take you there.

31
00:03:18,545 --> 00:03:20,265
-Go ahead.
-Yes.

32
00:03:36,385 --> 00:03:37,225
Father!

33
00:03:38,065 --> 00:03:39,425
Father!

34
00:04:02,265 --> 00:04:04,625
<i>Xie Yanfang is waiting to take advantage.</i>

35
00:04:05,145 --> 00:04:06,745
<i>Deng Yi is waiting</i>
<i>to profit from others' fight.</i>

36
00:04:08,505 --> 00:04:10,225
<i>Yet I have no idea</i>

37
00:04:10,305 --> 00:04:12,265
<i>about Father's physical condition.</i>

38
00:04:14,025 --> 00:04:15,945
<i>In my past life, as I recall,</i>

39
00:04:16,025 --> 00:04:18,225
<i>Father wasn't ill at this time.</i>

40
00:04:18,865 --> 00:04:21,184
<i>After my wedding,</i>
<i>the poisoned jujube cakes</i>

41
00:04:21,265 --> 00:04:23,025
<i>worsened his health.</i>

42
00:04:24,305 --> 00:04:26,305
<i>Did I neglect anything?</i>

43
00:04:30,625 --> 00:04:32,265
Your Highness, have some water.

44
00:04:41,505 --> 00:04:43,185
Your Highness, don't worry.

45
00:04:43,265 --> 00:04:44,425
Let me divine for you.

46
00:05:02,785 --> 00:05:03,745
It's all right.

47
00:05:04,265 --> 00:05:05,705
The crack points to the east.

48
00:05:05,785 --> 00:05:06,705
It's…

49
00:05:06,785 --> 00:05:08,425
an omen of misfortune
turning into fortune.

50
00:05:08,505 --> 00:05:10,345
Misfortune turning into fortune?

51
00:05:12,185 --> 00:05:14,265
So, misfortune comes first.

52
00:05:17,665 --> 00:05:20,945
Le, go send a letter to Chu Tang.

53
00:05:21,465 --> 00:05:23,105
Then have someone come to see me.

54
00:05:31,825 --> 00:05:34,225
Thank you for coming with me tonight.

55
00:05:34,305 --> 00:05:35,745
Take them to buy some drinks.

56
00:05:44,545 --> 00:05:45,705
Mr. Xie.

57
00:05:48,505 --> 00:05:49,345
Her Highness summoned you.

58
00:05:51,785 --> 00:05:52,745
<i>I'm going back to Yunzhong.</i>

59
00:05:54,025 --> 00:05:55,505
Do you know the consequences

60
00:05:56,385 --> 00:05:57,825
of leaving here without permission?

61
00:05:58,665 --> 00:05:59,745
I do.

62
00:06:00,785 --> 00:06:02,665
Deng Yi and Xie Yanfang
will get suspicious.

63
00:06:03,625 --> 00:06:06,585
When Le traveled around,
she met many Taoist physicians

64
00:06:06,665 --> 00:06:07,625
and got a prescription.

65
00:06:08,305 --> 00:06:09,665
Take it, and I'll faint from a high fever.

66
00:06:09,745 --> 00:06:10,785
My pulse will seem seriously weak.

67
00:06:11,465 --> 00:06:13,905
Then, Yu will give an order

68
00:06:13,985 --> 00:06:15,145
that nobody shall visit me.

69
00:06:16,945 --> 00:06:18,665
I won't let anyone disturb you.

70
00:06:25,305 --> 00:06:27,225
Le, take His Majesty to rest.

71
00:06:28,065 --> 00:06:28,945
Yes, Your Highness.

72
00:06:34,545 --> 00:06:36,545
If I feign illness and stay indoors,

73
00:06:36,625 --> 00:06:38,505
it'll just work out
in the ministers' favor.

74
00:06:39,265 --> 00:06:42,345
No one will verify if I'm truly ill.

75
00:06:42,425 --> 00:06:43,865
This is what they wish to see.

76
00:06:43,945 --> 00:06:46,225
How long can you hide this from those two?

77
00:06:46,945 --> 00:06:48,905
And Xiao Xun is back in his prefecture.

78
00:06:49,945 --> 00:06:51,305
If he gets to know about it,

79
00:06:52,345 --> 00:06:54,305
he won't allow you
to return to the frontier.

80
00:06:58,385 --> 00:06:59,425
Have you

81
00:07:00,745 --> 00:07:01,665
thought about all this?

82
00:07:03,425 --> 00:07:04,545
I have.

83
00:07:06,625 --> 00:07:08,305
Just because Xiao Xun is away…

84
00:07:12,745 --> 00:07:13,905
then I can leave.

85
00:07:16,465 --> 00:07:17,585
Since you stay in the court,

86
00:07:19,025 --> 00:07:20,705
I want to make it a quick trip.

87
00:07:24,505 --> 00:07:25,345
Jiu,

88
00:07:26,465 --> 00:07:27,585
help me.

89
00:07:40,545 --> 00:07:42,585
In the dream I told you about,

90
00:07:47,345 --> 00:07:49,105
my father was covered in blood.

91
00:07:52,985 --> 00:07:55,665
I want to make sure
my father is doing well.

92
00:07:59,865 --> 00:08:01,465
I have a lot of things

93
00:08:03,825 --> 00:08:04,945
to say to him.

94
00:08:06,465 --> 00:08:08,225
I don't want to have regrets

95
00:08:09,225 --> 00:08:10,185
in the future.

96
00:08:12,265 --> 00:08:14,065
You know how it feels when regrets

97
00:08:15,265 --> 00:08:16,465
can never be mended.

98
00:08:17,825 --> 00:08:18,985
Right?

99
00:08:44,105 --> 00:08:45,225
I'm still worried.

100
00:08:46,585 --> 00:08:47,545
You know…

101
00:08:49,425 --> 00:08:50,625
you can't stop me.

102
00:08:56,305 --> 00:09:01,745
CAPITAL

103
00:09:11,625 --> 00:09:13,825
Since when have you been so indecisive?

104
00:09:14,905 --> 00:09:16,705
You've escorted me over 30 li.

105
00:09:17,305 --> 00:09:19,865
Don't tell me you hate to part with me.

106
00:09:33,105 --> 00:09:34,185
Rest assured.

107
00:09:34,265 --> 00:09:35,865
My martial arts are mediocre,

108
00:09:36,385 --> 00:09:37,785
but I do practice every day.

109
00:09:40,305 --> 00:09:43,025
Your martial skills are no match

110
00:09:43,545 --> 00:09:44,465
for real masters.

111
00:09:47,825 --> 00:09:49,505
You wretched woman!

112
00:09:49,585 --> 00:09:51,225
Where do you think you can run to?

113
00:09:51,305 --> 00:09:53,625
I gave you food and drink,

114
00:09:53,705 --> 00:09:56,105
but you eloped with a man, didn't you?

115
00:09:56,185 --> 00:09:57,665
I'll break your legs!

116
00:10:04,185 --> 00:10:05,185
Spare my life, sir.

117
00:10:05,785 --> 00:10:07,905
I mistook you for someone else.

118
00:10:08,465 --> 00:10:13,105
Your carriage looks so much
like the one I'm looking for.

119
00:10:13,185 --> 00:10:15,345
I didn't recognize you

120
00:10:15,425 --> 00:10:16,985
and then offended you.

121
00:10:17,585 --> 00:10:18,785
Mistook us?

122
00:10:18,865 --> 00:10:21,305
Who are you really after?

123
00:10:21,385 --> 00:10:23,425
I run a pleasure house in Wuyang Town.

124
00:10:23,505 --> 00:10:24,985
My top courtesan

125
00:10:25,065 --> 00:10:27,265
ran off with a scholar
who went to the Capital.

126
00:10:27,345 --> 00:10:29,465
I came here to catch her.

127
00:10:30,065 --> 00:10:32,105
Unexpectedly, I stopped
the wrong carriage.

128
00:10:32,705 --> 00:10:34,145
I beg you to let me go.

129
00:10:34,225 --> 00:10:35,545
I don't want to die.

130
00:10:36,145 --> 00:10:37,065
Stop pretending.

131
00:10:37,785 --> 00:10:39,105
Who sent you?

132
00:10:39,625 --> 00:10:40,705
No one sent me.

133
00:10:40,785 --> 00:10:42,385
No one, really.

134
00:10:42,465 --> 00:10:44,185
I just got the wrong person.

135
00:10:44,265 --> 00:10:47,665
I don't want to die. Don't kill me.

136
00:10:50,585 --> 00:10:52,745
She doesn't seem to be lying.

137
00:10:53,905 --> 00:10:54,985
You may leave.

138
00:10:55,985 --> 00:10:57,385
Oh, thank you.

139
00:10:58,145 --> 00:10:59,385
Let's go.

140
00:11:04,145 --> 00:11:06,105
You're just like your father
in this aspect.

141
00:11:07,265 --> 00:11:08,825
You're both too trusting.

142
00:11:08,905 --> 00:11:10,025
When I was 14,

143
00:11:10,105 --> 00:11:12,265
I rode alone from Yunzhong to the Capital.

144
00:11:12,345 --> 00:11:13,905
I can tell good people from bad.

145
00:11:15,225 --> 00:11:16,425
I get it.

146
00:11:16,505 --> 00:11:17,705
But sometimes you can't.

147
00:11:18,225 --> 00:11:19,185
For example…

148
00:11:19,865 --> 00:11:20,945
Xiao Xun.

149
00:11:24,665 --> 00:11:25,785
Well, you're right.

150
00:11:26,305 --> 00:11:27,945
So what if I misjudged him?

151
00:11:28,465 --> 00:11:30,025
I fixed things, anyway.

152
00:11:30,865 --> 00:11:31,945
And I believe

153
00:11:32,905 --> 00:11:34,625
you won't let me get it wrong twice.

154
00:11:47,545 --> 00:11:48,545
Take this.

155
00:11:49,065 --> 00:11:50,265
Remember what I taught you.

156
00:11:52,865 --> 00:11:55,545
Didn't you say
my martial arts were useless?

157
00:11:57,185 --> 00:11:59,105
It's all right. I'm good at strategies.

158
00:12:06,545 --> 00:12:07,385
And this…

159
00:12:08,105 --> 00:12:09,345
You take it.

160
00:12:09,425 --> 00:12:11,305
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

161
00:12:11,905 --> 00:12:16,345
Do you know what
the Grand Princess Token means?

162
00:12:16,425 --> 00:12:17,705
It means

163
00:12:19,625 --> 00:12:20,465
I trust you.

164
00:12:30,105 --> 00:12:31,545
I'll keep it for now.

165
00:12:33,545 --> 00:12:34,625
And guard Yu for me.

166
00:12:37,505 --> 00:12:38,625
You…

167
00:12:41,345 --> 00:12:42,625
You take care.

168
00:13:00,745 --> 00:13:02,065
It's dark and far.

169
00:13:02,945 --> 00:13:04,265
Have a safe trip.

170
00:13:41,905 --> 00:13:45,065
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

171
00:13:49,945 --> 00:13:54,145
<i>Do you know what</i>
<i>the Grand Princess Token means?</i>

172
00:13:54,745 --> 00:13:55,865
<i>It means</i>

173
00:13:56,665 --> 00:13:57,705
<i>I trust you.</i>

174
00:14:15,785 --> 00:14:17,785
Your Highness, we got the news.

175
00:14:17,865 --> 00:14:19,425
Yesterday, the Grand Princess fell ill,

176
00:14:19,505 --> 00:14:20,705
had a fever, and skipped court.

177
00:14:28,705 --> 00:14:29,945
What a coincidence.

178
00:14:30,545 --> 00:14:31,785
Urgent news from Yunzhong

179
00:14:32,665 --> 00:14:34,185
said Chu Ling was gravely ill.

180
00:14:36,505 --> 00:14:39,065
I never expected the two of them

181
00:14:39,145 --> 00:14:40,945
to be so closely connected.

182
00:14:41,545 --> 00:14:42,985
If she left last night,

183
00:14:43,065 --> 00:14:44,625
I guess she's no longer in the Capital.

184
00:14:45,865 --> 00:14:47,945
Since she's out of town,

185
00:14:49,225 --> 00:14:50,425
I'll never let her go back.

186
00:14:51,425 --> 00:14:55,745
She'll pass through Wuyang Town
to Yunzhong.

187
00:14:55,825 --> 00:14:57,105
You…

188
00:14:57,185 --> 00:14:59,065
Have your men ambush outside town.

189
00:14:59,145 --> 00:15:00,785
Make sure that nothing goes wrong.

190
00:15:02,065 --> 00:15:03,105
I'm on it.

191
00:15:14,625 --> 00:15:15,865
Zhao.

192
00:15:23,305 --> 00:15:24,345
Stop the carriage.

193
00:15:28,665 --> 00:15:29,825
Where are we now?

194
00:15:29,905 --> 00:15:32,505
In half a day, we'll hit Wuyang Town.
Wait a minute.

195
00:15:32,585 --> 00:15:35,185
I'll hitch the horse
and tighten the reins.

196
00:15:36,065 --> 00:15:37,505
<i>As far as I know about Xiao Xun,</i>

197
00:15:38,025 --> 00:15:42,145
<i>he will make a move</i>
<i>upon receiving word of my illness.</i>

198
00:15:42,225 --> 00:15:44,105
<i>His men must be searching the town.</i>

199
00:15:44,705 --> 00:15:46,585
<i>This carriage is far too conspicuous.</i>

200
00:15:46,665 --> 00:15:47,505
<i>That's not safe.</i>

201
00:15:49,585 --> 00:15:51,105
Drop me off ten li outside the town

202
00:15:51,185 --> 00:15:53,545
and you go northwest
along the official road.

203
00:15:53,625 --> 00:15:55,145
Remember. You must not stop.

204
00:15:55,945 --> 00:15:57,065
All right.

205
00:16:05,465 --> 00:16:08,145
WUYANG TOWN

206
00:16:21,825 --> 00:16:22,945
<i>Just as I expected.</i>

207
00:16:23,025 --> 00:16:25,945
TEA

208
00:16:29,465 --> 00:16:30,705
Madam,

209
00:16:31,265 --> 00:16:33,065
those men don't look like good folks.

210
00:16:33,145 --> 00:16:34,425
What are they?

211
00:16:34,505 --> 00:16:35,705
Bandits?

212
00:16:36,225 --> 00:16:37,905
Don't say that.

213
00:16:37,985 --> 00:16:40,385
Our town has never
been plagued by bandits.

214
00:16:41,025 --> 00:16:43,225
They are the guards of a squire.

215
00:16:43,305 --> 00:16:46,145
I've heard a maid
stole valuables and ran off.

216
00:16:46,225 --> 00:16:47,505
Searching for a maid?

217
00:16:47,585 --> 00:16:48,825
Exactly.

218
00:16:48,905 --> 00:16:51,105
Their leader is really fierce.

219
00:16:51,185 --> 00:16:52,625
He even lifts up the veil
of the ladies' hats.

220
00:16:55,145 --> 00:16:56,665
Madam, get me some tea.

221
00:16:57,265 --> 00:16:58,265
Coming.

222
00:17:17,345 --> 00:17:18,305
Mr. Deng,

223
00:17:18,385 --> 00:17:20,345
Her Highness is resting.
She won't see anyone.

224
00:17:20,424 --> 00:17:22,745
Her illness involves the court.

225
00:17:22,825 --> 00:17:24,825
It's my duty to check on her.

226
00:17:25,625 --> 00:17:26,825
Don't you dare disobey me.

227
00:17:28,145 --> 00:17:28,985
How daring!

228
00:17:29,065 --> 00:17:31,385
You have no authority
over the inner palace.

229
00:17:32,105 --> 00:17:33,025
Take one more step forward

230
00:17:33,665 --> 00:17:34,625
and my sword

231
00:17:35,465 --> 00:17:36,345
won't show mercy.

232
00:17:43,265 --> 00:17:44,265
Good.

233
00:17:45,465 --> 00:17:46,505
Very good.

234
00:17:47,145 --> 00:17:48,145
Mr. Xie,

235
00:17:49,025 --> 00:17:50,785
let's wait and see.

236
00:18:10,585 --> 00:18:11,785
For her,

237
00:18:13,345 --> 00:18:14,585
you even offended Deng Yi.

238
00:18:17,225 --> 00:18:18,345
It is merely my duty.

239
00:18:19,545 --> 00:18:20,585
Far from offending.

240
00:18:22,665 --> 00:18:24,385
Tie Ying left Xiaonan

241
00:18:24,905 --> 00:18:26,665
and laid ambushes all the way to Yunzhong.

242
00:18:28,065 --> 00:18:28,905
Do you really think

243
00:18:29,825 --> 00:18:31,025
she can reach the frontier alive?

244
00:18:32,425 --> 00:18:34,585
She's stronger than you think.

245
00:18:39,665 --> 00:18:42,545
Right. She's exceptionally smart.

246
00:18:43,185 --> 00:18:46,025
But even if she can survive
Xiao Xun's ambushes,

247
00:18:46,825 --> 00:18:48,705
she has forgotten something.

248
00:18:50,345 --> 00:18:52,705
Bandits run rampant
along the way to the frontier.

249
00:18:53,745 --> 00:18:55,545
I'm afraid other dangers

250
00:18:56,865 --> 00:18:58,425
are lying ahead for her.

251
00:19:00,385 --> 00:19:02,145
She's a woman, after all.

252
00:19:02,225 --> 00:19:04,745
If she happens to run into those outlaws,

253
00:19:05,345 --> 00:19:06,545
how many miles

254
00:19:07,665 --> 00:19:09,505
do you think she can survive?

255
00:19:11,465 --> 00:19:12,505
Yanlai,

256
00:19:13,065 --> 00:19:15,305
guard the imperial city well.

257
00:19:15,905 --> 00:19:18,425
Otherwise, when the news
of her death comes,

258
00:19:19,985 --> 00:19:22,025
no one will hold a funeral for her.

259
00:19:34,585 --> 00:19:35,865
You wretched woman!

260
00:19:35,945 --> 00:19:37,345
You ran away one by one.

261
00:19:37,425 --> 00:19:39,785
Why? Didn't I feed you
or buy you nice clothes?

262
00:19:39,865 --> 00:19:42,225
I bought you with 20 liang of silver!

263
00:19:42,305 --> 00:19:44,425
If you just… Watch where you're going!

264
00:19:49,865 --> 00:19:50,705
We meet again.

265
00:19:55,825 --> 00:19:56,945
Move aside.

266
00:19:57,985 --> 00:20:00,065
My Lord, carriage tracks northwest.

267
00:20:00,145 --> 00:20:01,385
It has special horseshoe markings,

268
00:20:01,465 --> 00:20:03,025
like those of the Capital.

269
00:20:03,105 --> 00:20:04,385
Report!

270
00:20:05,425 --> 00:20:07,025
Behind the north dune, we found this,

271
00:20:07,105 --> 00:20:09,065
with "Zhao" on it.
I think it's from a noble lady.

272
00:20:10,345 --> 00:20:12,305
Report!

273
00:20:12,385 --> 00:20:13,985
Northeast, a woman hired a guard escort

274
00:20:14,065 --> 00:20:15,265
to send her to the frontier.

275
00:20:15,345 --> 00:20:16,665
She splurged a lot.

276
00:20:17,785 --> 00:20:19,025
Three traces.

277
00:20:19,865 --> 00:20:21,145
She left false clues, huh?

278
00:20:22,145 --> 00:20:23,465
Pass my order.

279
00:20:23,545 --> 00:20:26,105
Go three ways.
Northwest, north, and northeast.

280
00:20:26,185 --> 00:20:27,705
Pursue all of them.

281
00:20:27,785 --> 00:20:30,665
My Lord, if we pursue rashly, I'm afraid…

282
00:20:30,745 --> 00:20:32,425
Better kill the innocent than let them go.

283
00:20:33,025 --> 00:20:35,145
Every suspicious woman must be arrested.

284
00:20:35,225 --> 00:20:36,345
Yes.

285
00:20:44,745 --> 00:20:47,905
BEICAO POST HOUSE

286
00:20:49,425 --> 00:20:50,265
It is good.

287
00:20:50,345 --> 00:20:52,145
-The beef tastes good.
-Postmaster,

288
00:20:52,225 --> 00:20:53,905
the post house is small,

289
00:20:53,985 --> 00:20:55,385
but you offer very good service.

290
00:20:55,465 --> 00:20:57,105
You deliver messages to Yunzhong.

291
00:20:57,185 --> 00:20:58,465
The journey must be rough.

292
00:20:58,545 --> 00:21:00,265
This post house is just like a home.

293
00:21:00,345 --> 00:21:01,785
Right? You deserve nice food.

294
00:21:03,425 --> 00:21:05,985
Who is this girl? She isn't a local, huh?

295
00:21:06,585 --> 00:21:07,945
She's a poor girl.

296
00:21:08,465 --> 00:21:10,145
Her father worked at the frontier.

297
00:21:10,225 --> 00:21:12,465
She and her mother
came all the way for him.

298
00:21:12,545 --> 00:21:13,825
Sadly, on their way,

299
00:21:13,905 --> 00:21:15,985
her mother fell gravely ill.

300
00:21:16,065 --> 00:21:17,665
Obviously, she's going to…

301
00:21:18,865 --> 00:21:20,905
Officers, please take me to Yunzhong.

302
00:21:21,945 --> 00:21:24,785
-I want to see my father.
-But…

303
00:21:25,745 --> 00:21:27,745
It's urgent news. We must not delay.

304
00:21:27,825 --> 00:21:29,425
Officers, this girl is sensible.

305
00:21:29,505 --> 00:21:31,425
During the trip, she won't bring trouble.

306
00:21:31,505 --> 00:21:33,825
There in Yunzhong,
General Chu commands strictly.

307
00:21:33,905 --> 00:21:35,705
When he knows you've helped someone,

308
00:21:35,785 --> 00:21:37,865
maybe you'll be given credit for this.

309
00:21:37,945 --> 00:21:38,905
What do you think?

310
00:21:42,025 --> 00:21:44,505
We're dispatch riders from Wangcheng Camp.

311
00:21:44,585 --> 00:21:47,265
We've met General Chu a few times.

312
00:21:48,065 --> 00:21:49,225
Head up.

313
00:21:51,865 --> 00:21:53,625
There are many troops at the frontier.

314
00:21:54,145 --> 00:21:56,065
Tell me your name and background.

315
00:21:56,665 --> 00:21:58,585
-She is--
-Let her speak.

316
00:22:02,185 --> 00:22:03,665
My name is Fu.

317
00:22:04,265 --> 00:22:06,105
My father is Yang Dachun.

318
00:22:06,985 --> 00:22:10,225
He serves at Saishang Outpost
in Daqing Mountain Camp,

319
00:22:10,305 --> 00:22:12,105
under General Chu Ling's command.

320
00:22:16,305 --> 00:22:18,225
This is my father's letter.

321
00:22:22,705 --> 00:22:23,985
His handwriting is good.

322
00:22:36,385 --> 00:22:37,585
Take us to see your mother.

323
00:22:37,665 --> 00:22:39,585
If you're telling the truth,

324
00:22:39,665 --> 00:22:40,825
we'll take you along.

325
00:22:41,985 --> 00:22:43,505
Get up. Come on.

326
00:22:44,665 --> 00:22:45,585
I'll take you to see her.

327
00:22:47,425 --> 00:22:48,825
Mother. Mother.

328
00:22:48,905 --> 00:22:50,745
Some officers will head for Father's camp.

329
00:22:50,825 --> 00:22:53,265
Mother. Mother. Mother.

330
00:22:54,505 --> 00:22:55,465
Mother.

331
00:22:58,225 --> 00:22:59,385
Mother.

332
00:23:01,425 --> 00:23:02,705
Have some water.

333
00:23:05,825 --> 00:23:06,985
Officers,

334
00:23:07,505 --> 00:23:10,105
are you heading for Daqing Mountain Camp?

335
00:23:10,185 --> 00:23:11,385
No.

336
00:23:11,905 --> 00:23:12,945
But we'll pass by.

337
00:23:14,945 --> 00:23:18,025
What's your husband's name?

338
00:23:18,545 --> 00:23:19,385
How old is he?

339
00:23:20,305 --> 00:23:21,505
Who does he work for?

340
00:23:22,865 --> 00:23:25,105
-You asked just now.
-Let her answer.

341
00:23:32,265 --> 00:23:33,305
My husband…

342
00:23:35,465 --> 00:23:36,465
is Yang Dachun.

343
00:23:37,545 --> 00:23:38,985
The seventh day of the third month.

344
00:23:39,505 --> 00:23:41,185
He serves under General Chu.

345
00:23:43,945 --> 00:23:45,385
Mother. Mother.

346
00:23:46,065 --> 00:23:46,945
I…

347
00:23:48,465 --> 00:23:49,465
I made him…

348
00:23:50,105 --> 00:23:51,185
a pair of new shoes.

349
00:23:52,625 --> 00:23:53,465
Fu,

350
00:23:54,545 --> 00:23:55,985
promise me you will

351
00:23:56,505 --> 00:23:59,105
give the shoes to your father.

352
00:24:04,145 --> 00:24:05,625
Let me be blunt.

353
00:24:06,145 --> 00:24:07,905
Our mission is urgent.

354
00:24:07,985 --> 00:24:09,425
The journey will be tough and swift.

355
00:24:09,505 --> 00:24:10,865
Young girl,

356
00:24:11,385 --> 00:24:13,585
keep up if you can.

357
00:24:13,665 --> 00:24:16,225
If you can't, we'll leave you behind.

358
00:24:17,185 --> 00:24:18,545
Officers,

359
00:24:18,625 --> 00:24:21,465
take her as far as you can.

360
00:24:22,265 --> 00:24:24,985
The closer she gets to her father,

361
00:24:25,065 --> 00:24:29,305
the sooner her father will find her.

362
00:24:30,065 --> 00:24:32,985
Fu, kowtow and thank them.

363
00:24:34,865 --> 00:24:36,265
Thank you, officers.

364
00:24:37,865 --> 00:24:38,745
Mother.

365
00:24:41,545 --> 00:24:42,785
-Enough.
-Mother.

366
00:24:42,865 --> 00:24:44,545
Tomorrow morning, we'll set off.

367
00:24:47,025 --> 00:24:48,425
Officers!

368
00:24:49,465 --> 00:24:52,665
If you manage to see my husband,

369
00:24:52,745 --> 00:24:54,905
please tell him

370
00:24:54,985 --> 00:24:58,065
I am blessed
to be his wife all these years.

371
00:24:59,065 --> 00:25:00,825
My life is worth it.

372
00:25:01,585 --> 00:25:02,825
Mother.

373
00:25:06,025 --> 00:25:08,865
Life is so hard. So hard.

374
00:25:09,465 --> 00:25:10,865
My poor girl.

375
00:25:12,705 --> 00:25:13,665
Get packed.

376
00:25:13,745 --> 00:25:15,945
Our schedule is fixed.
We can't stay too long.

377
00:25:18,145 --> 00:25:19,225
This way.

378
00:25:20,225 --> 00:25:23,065
Life is so cruel to us!

379
00:25:23,785 --> 00:25:26,825
Oh, so cruel.

380
00:25:28,705 --> 00:25:30,585
So cruel.

381
00:25:39,825 --> 00:25:42,545
Is there a girl who has my figure?

382
00:25:44,025 --> 00:25:45,665
Oh, I see.

383
00:25:45,745 --> 00:25:49,025
So you want a substitute.

384
00:25:50,985 --> 00:25:51,865
That's hard.

385
00:25:52,465 --> 00:25:53,465
Look at you.

386
00:25:53,545 --> 00:25:55,865
You're slender and tall.

387
00:25:55,945 --> 00:25:58,545
Ordinary girls
wouldn't be as great as you.

388
00:25:59,825 --> 00:26:01,945
There are. As many as you want.

389
00:26:03,505 --> 00:26:05,025
Then, do you have children?

390
00:26:07,785 --> 00:26:10,265
Just now, why did you add something extra?

391
00:26:12,545 --> 00:26:14,425
I'm "dying".

392
00:26:14,505 --> 00:26:16,785
When I missed your father
and recalled our old days,

393
00:26:16,865 --> 00:26:21,385
that was natural, uncontrollable,
and touching.

394
00:26:21,905 --> 00:26:23,105
You're too young.

395
00:26:23,185 --> 00:26:24,625
When it comes to love,

396
00:26:24,705 --> 00:26:26,585
I'm more experienced, after all.

397
00:26:26,665 --> 00:26:29,345
A frontier soldier's wife
wouldn't speak such sentimental words.

398
00:26:34,985 --> 00:26:36,705
Fine. It's my fault. Come on.

399
00:26:37,625 --> 00:26:40,865
Tomorrow, will you really
follow those riders?

400
00:26:41,385 --> 00:26:42,345
Will they see through you?

401
00:26:42,425 --> 00:26:43,865
Of course I will.

402
00:26:46,585 --> 00:26:48,825
Because I've noticed their secret.

403
00:26:50,145 --> 00:26:50,985
What secret?

404
00:26:54,905 --> 00:26:56,905
XIE RESIDENCE

405
00:27:13,025 --> 00:27:16,585
Yanlai, why do you act like a thief
in your own home?

406
00:27:17,305 --> 00:27:18,625
I have a favor to ask.

407
00:27:20,625 --> 00:27:21,465
Keep it between us.

408
00:27:22,385 --> 00:27:24,065
How strange.

409
00:27:24,665 --> 00:27:27,705
I never thought you would ask for a favor.

410
00:27:31,945 --> 00:27:32,905
Help me leave the Capital.

411
00:27:34,945 --> 00:27:36,745
As the Imperial Guard Commander,

412
00:27:37,745 --> 00:27:39,025
you mustn't desert your post.

413
00:27:39,985 --> 00:27:41,065
It's the rule.

414
00:27:41,785 --> 00:27:43,105
You know it better than me.

415
00:27:43,785 --> 00:27:44,985
You're right.

416
00:27:46,145 --> 00:27:47,985
The trip to Yunzhong is very dangerous.

417
00:27:49,025 --> 00:27:50,665
She holds a unique status.

418
00:27:50,745 --> 00:27:51,865
If anything happens…

419
00:27:53,505 --> 00:27:54,425
Yanlai,

420
00:27:55,545 --> 00:27:57,345
I've never seen you

421
00:27:58,905 --> 00:28:00,385
care about someone like this.

422
00:28:07,385 --> 00:28:09,505
The Grand Princess affords
to feign illness.

423
00:28:10,145 --> 00:28:12,145
It's not easy for you

424
00:28:12,825 --> 00:28:14,505
to leave.

425
00:28:16,465 --> 00:28:17,705
Have you thought it through?

426
00:28:23,945 --> 00:28:25,025
If you help me,

427
00:28:27,705 --> 00:28:29,105
I'll owe you one.

428
00:28:39,265 --> 00:28:41,305
Food and water bags are ready.

429
00:28:41,385 --> 00:28:42,705
Take care.

430
00:28:43,305 --> 00:28:44,505
Thank you.

431
00:28:44,585 --> 00:28:46,465
And I'll trouble you
to take care of my mother.

432
00:28:46,545 --> 00:28:47,745
BEICAO POST HOUSE

433
00:28:47,825 --> 00:28:48,945
Count on me.

434
00:29:02,825 --> 00:29:04,465
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

435
00:29:05,585 --> 00:29:06,825
Stop playing.

436
00:29:06,905 --> 00:29:08,505
You haven't finished your lessons.

437
00:29:08,585 --> 00:29:10,225
If the Grand Mentor finds out…

438
00:29:11,545 --> 00:29:12,985
Leave me alone.

439
00:29:13,785 --> 00:29:17,385
If you still nag, I'll order you
to catch a hundred crickets.

440
00:29:22,745 --> 00:29:23,865
Why aren't you studying?

441
00:29:28,185 --> 00:29:29,265
Uncle, you're just in time.

442
00:29:29,865 --> 00:29:32,185
Look. The cricket in my cage

443
00:29:32,265 --> 00:29:33,705
is far funnier than the Analects.

444
00:29:34,665 --> 00:29:35,625
Your Majesty,

445
00:29:36,905 --> 00:29:39,905
the Imperial Study is no place for fun.

446
00:29:44,105 --> 00:29:45,105
How dare you throw away my cricket!

447
00:29:47,345 --> 00:29:48,345
Your Majesty.

448
00:29:48,425 --> 00:29:50,425
Xie Yanlai, how daring!
You pushed me over!

449
00:29:51,945 --> 00:29:53,065
Your Majesty.

450
00:29:53,585 --> 00:29:55,025
Mr. Xie, how could you do this?

451
00:29:57,065 --> 00:29:59,505
Commander Xie Yanlai misbehaved

452
00:29:59,585 --> 00:30:01,385
and pushed His Majesty over.

453
00:30:01,465 --> 00:30:03,305
This is blatant disrespect.

454
00:30:03,385 --> 00:30:06,225
If such behavior is allowed,
all rules will be gone.

455
00:30:06,305 --> 00:30:08,145
You're exaggerating, Mr. Deng.

456
00:30:08,785 --> 00:30:10,305
My brother has been respectful.

457
00:30:10,385 --> 00:30:12,505
He serves His Majesty devotedly.

458
00:30:13,105 --> 00:30:14,545
His Majesty is young and playful.

459
00:30:14,625 --> 00:30:19,025
Maybe as they played around,
my brother just slipped up.

460
00:30:19,105 --> 00:30:20,905
Are you suggesting

461
00:30:21,505 --> 00:30:24,625
His Majesty is slandering a minister?

462
00:30:24,705 --> 00:30:25,705
How dare I?

463
00:30:25,785 --> 00:30:29,065
The Imperial Guard Commander
secures the imperial city.

464
00:30:29,145 --> 00:30:31,665
If he's punished for stopping His Majesty

465
00:30:31,745 --> 00:30:32,865
from playing too much,

466
00:30:33,465 --> 00:30:35,905
the soldiers will be disheartened.

467
00:30:35,985 --> 00:30:37,585
You really defend your brother.

468
00:30:38,265 --> 00:30:40,665
The Grand Princess has been absent.

469
00:30:40,745 --> 00:30:42,505
The Imperial Guards are so arrogant.

470
00:30:43,105 --> 00:30:44,945
Mr. Xie, do you think

471
00:30:45,025 --> 00:30:46,945
there is no restraint

472
00:30:47,465 --> 00:30:48,985
for the court?

473
00:30:52,065 --> 00:30:53,785
Don't drag Her Highness into this.

474
00:30:54,465 --> 00:30:55,665
She hasn't recovered yet.

475
00:30:55,745 --> 00:30:58,985
His Majesty cares for her
and grants her a quiet recovery.

476
00:30:59,585 --> 00:31:00,825
As for the restraint…

477
00:31:01,625 --> 00:31:03,505
You govern for His Majesty.

478
00:31:03,585 --> 00:31:05,465
Isn't it the greatest restraint?

479
00:31:05,545 --> 00:31:06,745
Enough!

480
00:31:07,985 --> 00:31:09,945
Xie Yanlai disrespected me!

481
00:31:10,025 --> 00:31:11,705
He'll be suspended for reflection!

482
00:31:11,785 --> 00:31:12,825
Grand Mentor!

483
00:31:13,705 --> 00:31:15,145
Draft the edict for me.

484
00:31:15,665 --> 00:31:17,025
How wise, Your Majesty.

485
00:31:17,625 --> 00:31:19,585
The Imperial Guards need a leader.

486
00:31:19,665 --> 00:31:21,185
I recommend

487
00:31:21,705 --> 00:31:24,265
-the deputy commander to fill in.
-Don't bother.

488
00:31:24,865 --> 00:31:26,145
I'll select candidates

489
00:31:26,665 --> 00:31:28,865
to handle Imperial Guard affairs.

490
00:31:28,945 --> 00:31:30,945
His Majesty will decide.

491
00:31:31,025 --> 00:31:34,185
Just do it as you wish.
I'm tired. Court is dismissed!

492
00:31:35,545 --> 00:31:38,265
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.

493
00:31:58,105 --> 00:31:58,865
‎TAIJI HALL

494
00:31:58,945 --> 00:32:00,665
<i>Fu Jiu, the Imperial Guard Commander,</i>

495
00:32:00,745 --> 00:32:02,065
<i>offended His Majesty.</i>

496
00:32:02,145 --> 00:32:05,265
<i>He got suspended from post.</i>

497
00:32:12,385 --> 00:32:13,425
Yanlai.

498
00:32:13,505 --> 00:32:14,465
ONE DAY AGO

499
00:32:14,545 --> 00:32:16,545
His Majesty wants this letter
to Her Highness.

500
00:32:17,225 --> 00:32:18,465
I'm quite curious.

501
00:32:18,985 --> 00:32:21,065
How has the Grand Princess fascinated you?

502
00:32:25,065 --> 00:32:26,345
Over the past five years,

503
00:32:29,745 --> 00:32:30,905
I never owed anyone.

504
00:32:30,985 --> 00:32:33,385
Do you trust me with Yu just like that?

505
00:32:34,185 --> 00:32:36,465
In the imperial city,
many fierce forces are lurking.

506
00:32:39,505 --> 00:32:41,145
He can only be entrusted to you.

507
00:32:42,665 --> 00:32:43,945
He's of Xie Family's bloodline

508
00:32:44,705 --> 00:32:46,225
and your own nephew.

509
00:32:49,945 --> 00:32:51,265
Then give me

510
00:32:52,065 --> 00:32:53,345
the Grand Princess Token.

511
00:32:55,465 --> 00:32:56,785
If she trusts you,

512
00:32:58,025 --> 00:32:58,865
she must have given it.

513
00:33:02,185 --> 00:33:03,705
The enemy is before us.

514
00:33:05,185 --> 00:33:06,945
You should know what matters most.

515
00:33:08,065 --> 00:33:09,945
Now, the court is ruled by three forces.

516
00:33:10,665 --> 00:33:12,305
Deng Yi drafts edicts.

517
00:33:12,385 --> 00:33:13,705
I review the edicts.

518
00:33:14,305 --> 00:33:17,145
Without the Grand Princess's approval,
no ministries shall seal them.

519
00:33:18,105 --> 00:33:19,225
I give you my word.

520
00:33:19,305 --> 00:33:21,665
I will protect Yu at any cost.

521
00:33:22,905 --> 00:33:24,625
I know what worries you.

522
00:33:25,825 --> 00:33:27,385
But don't forget.

523
00:33:27,985 --> 00:33:31,105
The Token can only stop Deng Yi
from issuing unauthorized edicts.

524
00:33:32,305 --> 00:33:33,185
It has no other use.

525
00:33:34,065 --> 00:33:35,945
Even if I have a plan with it,

526
00:33:36,025 --> 00:33:38,385
I won't succeed
without Deng Yi's Imperial Seal.

527
00:33:39,865 --> 00:33:40,985
The token will just

528
00:33:41,065 --> 00:33:43,065
make it easier to counterbalance

529
00:33:43,145 --> 00:33:44,385
Deng Yi and me.

530
00:33:45,345 --> 00:33:47,705
So, Yanlai, don't doubt my intentions.

531
00:33:48,305 --> 00:33:49,785
Besides,

532
00:33:50,385 --> 00:33:51,945
with nothing to trade,

533
00:33:52,025 --> 00:33:55,065
how could I willingly agree to your terms?

534
00:34:13,865 --> 00:34:15,425
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

535
00:34:15,505 --> 00:34:17,705
CAPITAL

536
00:34:34,905 --> 00:34:37,905
Xie Yanlai, the pawn, is out of the game,

537
00:34:37,985 --> 00:34:41,744
leaving the state to you and Xie Yanfang.

538
00:34:43,185 --> 00:34:46,465
Aren't you going
to set up a scheme of loyalty

539
00:34:46,545 --> 00:34:48,025
when the emperor's still young?

540
00:34:49,105 --> 00:34:50,344
When Xiao Yu was little,

541
00:34:51,025 --> 00:34:52,505
he was badly frightened.

542
00:34:53,145 --> 00:34:54,304
Once the crowd grows,

543
00:34:54,385 --> 00:34:56,385
he always hides behind Chu Zhao.

544
00:34:59,105 --> 00:35:00,305
Wait.

545
00:35:01,985 --> 00:35:03,345
Chu Zhao has left.

546
00:35:03,425 --> 00:35:04,665
Xie Yanlai is suspended.

547
00:35:05,705 --> 00:35:07,345
What's in it for Xie Yanfang?

548
00:35:09,145 --> 00:35:11,105
In today's court,

549
00:35:11,625 --> 00:35:13,265
he seemed happy about that.

550
00:35:16,945 --> 00:35:18,505
You're really something, Xie Yanfang.

551
00:35:19,025 --> 00:35:20,385
Only now have I realized

552
00:35:20,905 --> 00:35:23,545
that you used me to complete your game.

553
00:35:24,105 --> 00:35:28,345
Is he plotting something
against the emperor?

554
00:35:28,945 --> 00:35:30,105
It doesn't matter.

555
00:35:31,505 --> 00:35:34,025
Xie Yanfang is an uncle in name only.

556
00:35:34,745 --> 00:35:36,545
His Majesty is distant from him.

557
00:35:36,625 --> 00:35:37,825
They won't get close.

558
00:35:37,905 --> 00:35:40,305
What if he makes the first move

559
00:35:41,265 --> 00:35:42,985
to catch us off guard?

560
00:35:44,905 --> 00:35:46,065
Don't worry.

561
00:35:46,585 --> 00:35:47,825
He dare not act rashly.

562
00:35:49,145 --> 00:35:50,985
After all, in the court game,

563
00:35:52,385 --> 00:35:53,825
we like to seize the initiative

564
00:35:57,065 --> 00:35:57,985
and fear making a misstep.

565
00:35:58,065 --> 00:35:59,385
However,

566
00:36:00,385 --> 00:36:01,985
if Chu Ling dies,

567
00:36:02,505 --> 00:36:04,385
Northern Desert soldiers
will march straight here.

568
00:36:04,465 --> 00:36:05,745
By then,

569
00:36:06,465 --> 00:36:09,505
neither you nor the Xie Family
can get away without losses.

570
00:36:10,025 --> 00:36:11,305
You're right.

571
00:36:12,065 --> 00:36:13,305
So, in this game,

572
00:36:13,825 --> 00:36:15,785
we're not sure what we'll do next.

573
00:36:16,305 --> 00:36:17,905
But we both know

574
00:36:19,385 --> 00:36:21,425
that Chu Ling must not die now.

575
00:36:31,225 --> 00:36:33,105
Xie Yanlai left town
at the first quarter of the Shen hour.

576
00:36:33,185 --> 00:36:35,665
He rode your favorite Dark Steed.

577
00:36:35,745 --> 00:36:37,145
Calculated by speed,

578
00:36:37,225 --> 00:36:39,825
he must have reached Beicao Town.

579
00:36:39,905 --> 00:36:41,545
He was quite obedient.

580
00:36:42,065 --> 00:36:43,745
He didn't even suspect

581
00:36:43,825 --> 00:36:45,425
the horse I gave him.

582
00:36:45,505 --> 00:36:46,945
How would he?

583
00:36:47,025 --> 00:36:48,905
You gave him your best horse.

584
00:36:48,985 --> 00:36:50,065
He should be grateful.

585
00:36:51,385 --> 00:36:53,265
Well, he was sensible this time.

586
00:36:53,865 --> 00:36:55,665
He did give you the Token.

587
00:36:57,585 --> 00:36:59,745
This token isn't of much use.

588
00:37:00,345 --> 00:37:01,705
But it works very well

589
00:37:02,225 --> 00:37:03,825
to trouble Deng Yi.

590
00:37:03,905 --> 00:37:04,985
But

591
00:37:05,065 --> 00:37:08,105
Xie Yanlai obviously has got feelings
for the Grand Princess.

592
00:37:08,185 --> 00:37:09,665
Do you think

593
00:37:10,265 --> 00:37:11,665
he'll get more out of our control?

594
00:37:16,065 --> 00:37:17,865
The best part of taming a baby wolf

595
00:37:18,385 --> 00:37:21,305
is to make it think
it has broken free from the collar.

596
00:37:22,225 --> 00:37:24,945
Actually, the collar
was replaced with gold cord.

597
00:37:25,625 --> 00:37:27,225
The harder he struggles,

598
00:37:27,745 --> 00:37:29,065
the tighter it binds him.

599
00:37:29,745 --> 00:37:32,105
He's risking his life to save Chu Zhao.

600
00:37:32,745 --> 00:37:34,585
He thinks he's resisting.

601
00:37:35,665 --> 00:37:38,425
Actually, he has revealed
his fatal weakness.

602
00:37:39,585 --> 00:37:41,385
He once told me

603
00:37:42,505 --> 00:37:43,905
Chu Zhao was very clever.

604
00:37:45,785 --> 00:37:48,865
I thought he lost his judgment,
driven by emotions.

605
00:37:52,305 --> 00:37:55,265
That woman behaves so clumsily
and anxiously.

606
00:37:58,025 --> 00:37:59,705
What makes her smart?

607
00:38:00,785 --> 00:38:02,585
Now I finally understand.

608
00:38:04,305 --> 00:38:05,785
Making Yanlai care so much about her

609
00:38:07,065 --> 00:38:09,465
proves her great wisdom.

610
00:38:14,185 --> 00:38:15,745
How foolish of me.

611
00:38:17,585 --> 00:38:18,585
I fail to realize…

612
00:38:18,665 --> 00:38:19,505
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

613
00:38:20,105 --> 00:38:22,425
…your subtle schemes.

